OL,3,CWater companies to invest more than
OL,4,C#180m to tackle sewage spills
OL,6,FWater companies are to invest more
OL,7,Fthan #180m to tackle sewage spills as
OL,8,Fpart of a fast-tracked investment in
OL,9,Foverflow prevention measures by April
OL,10,F2025.
OL,12,FThe investment includes artificial
OL,13,Fintelligence systems, accelerated
OL,14,Fwetland programmes, installing new in-
OL,15,Fsewer monitors and recruiting and
OL,16,Ftraining specialist staff.
OL,18,FThe government said it expects the
OL,19,Fmeasures to prevent more than 8,000
OL,20,Fspills polluting English waterways.
