OL,3,CWater companies to invest more than
OL,4,C#180m to tackle sewage spills
OL,6,FAnglian will invest #50 million,
OL,7,FSevern Trent will invest #41 million,
OL,8,FSouthern will invest #10 million,
OL,9,FSouth West will invest #32 million,
OL,10,FUnited Utilities will invest #39
OL,11,Fmillion and Wessex will invest #8
OL,12,Fmillion.
OL,14,FEnvironment Secretary Steve Barclay
OL,15,Fsaid the investment is part of
OL,16,Fgovernment efforts to "push for better
OL,17,Fperformance from water companies and
OL,18,Fhold them to account".
