OL,3,CWater companies to invest more than
OL,4,C#180m to tackle sewage spills
OL,6,FHe said: "The amount of sewage being
OL,7,Fspilled into our rivers is completely
OL,8,Funacceptable and the public rightly
OL,9,Fexpects action.
OL,11,F"This money will mean more cutting-
OL,12,Fedge technology, including artificial
OL,13,Fintelligence, and more specialist
OL,14,Fstaff to detect and reduce spills.
OL,16,F"Today's announcement builds on
OL,17,Fsignificant work by this Government to
OL,18,Fprotect and strengthen our waters with
OL,19,Fincreased investment, stronger
OL,20,Fregulation and tougher enforcement
OL,21,Faction."
