OL,3,CWater companies to invest more than
OL,4,C#180m to tackle sewage spills
OL,6,FThe investment will add to the water
OL,7,Fcompanies' previous #3.1 billion
OL,8,Finvestment for the period of 2020 to
OL,9,F2025.
OL,11,FIt is the latest move to tackle
OL,12,Fconcerns over levels of pollution
OL,13,Fbeing dumped into rivers, lakes and
OL,14,Faround the coasts from sources
OL,15,Fincluding overflow pipes and
OL,16,Fprocessing plants, causing harm to
OL,17,Fwildlife and the health of beachgoers
OL,18,Fas well as affecting tourism and
OL,19,Fleisure industries.
