OL,3,CWater companies to invest more than
OL,4,C#180m to tackle sewage spills
OL,6,FGiles Bristow, chief executive of
OL,7,FSurfers Against Sewage, said: "It's
OL,8,Fgreat to see the Government fast-
OL,9,Ftracking investment on the decades-old
OL,10,Fissue of sewage pollution.
OL,12,F"The informed and angry voices of
OL,13,Fconstituents across the UK are clearly
OL,14,Fmaking those in power listen and take
OL,15,Fvisible actions to address the sewage
OL,16,Fscandal.
OL,18,F"Despite today's welcome announcement,
OL,19,Fquestions still remain on the scale
OL,20,Fand scope of the Government's
OL,21,Fambitions for our rivers and seas.
